{"type": "article", "id": 23670, "title": "彩色置物盒设计", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-11T08:24:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606155041Ac3l9ekoCr0P8ZdH.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一组置物盒的概念设计，它是一个带抽屉的方框。方框和抽屉都是白色的，只在后面填充以不同的颜色，在整齐有序中带着一点活泼。方框本身是一个书架，它与书本、光碟、茶杯等带有装饰感的东西放在一起，组成有互动感的装饰。可以挂在墙上或罗列在地上，设计者是三位来自意大利的设计师，产品还是一个概念。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155039MpxoqaHw96v1X8tg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155040eF90nKNhUy5AiaBO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62638889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155040byZLdWo5lkM1sh0G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62638889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155041ayMYBmdErTfscjPA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62638889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}